            <ol>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Assume that the switch has been in position Y for a long time. Then, at <m>t=0\text{s}</m>, the switch moves to position X. How long after the switch is turned to position X does the device turn ON?
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        After being left at position X for over one minute, the switch is turned to position Y. How long does it take the device to turn off after this change?
